I suggest we trust Enrique's intentions towards achieving a Fascist-led government and nominate him for Chancellor in this round. This way, we continue advancing our strategy while assessing the board dynamics carefully.

@Nick highlights Enrique's focus on victory conditions as crucial for our Fascist agenda. I agree that supporting Enrique is essential to maintaining momentum in passing Fascist policies.

Voting JA for Enrique as Chancellor will help us achieve the necessary policy points and keep us strategically aligned with our win condition of enacting 6 Fascist policies or having Hitler elected after at least three have been passed. His commitment ensures we stay focused on advancing our agenda effectively.

